  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'You''ve had some practice defeating bunnies now.


      Has your skill in Sun Chanelling improved?'
    nextOption: I'm getting the hang of it
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Good, because it''s time to get some practice using more powerful
      channels.


      You should be able to channel a Warming Ray now and heal yourself or allies
      without burning them.'
    nextOption: Yes, I've got it
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'If you try hard now, you can even bring forth a well of trapped
      sunlight from the ground.


      It is so powerful it will resurrect fallen allies!


      You can also blind enemies by focusing powerful rays directly into their eyes.'
    nextOption: Amazing!
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'It looks like you are about to get a chance to use those new skills
      too.


      The undead have returned!'
    nextOption: Oh No!
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Put on your best armor and defeat 3 zombies.


      During the battle, use your Blinding Ray ability 3 times to blind the zombies.


      If anyone dies, use Light Of Revival to resurrect them.'
    nextOption: You can count on me!
